products.name: .Blink-182 ”Missionary Impossible” Tour – HOODIE
products.description:
T SHIRT AND POLO
  • Hand washable.
  • 2D 100% cotton
  • The tank tops with high quality 3D printed without fading, cracking and peeling. The high technology Made the print on sleeveless graphic tees crisp.
  • Suitable Occasion: Perfect for home, fitness, exercise, beach, surfing, ball games, running, jogging, tourism, holiday, music festivals, hip-hop time, parties, ect.
  • Men’s tank tops made of polyester and spandex, with good air permeabilityand and lightweight. Both machine and hand washable.

 

HOODIE AND ZIP HOODIE

This comfortable unisex pullover hoodie is thermal hoodie that is perfect to keep warm. The comfortable and unisex cut is suitable for both men and women. The unique pattern of high quality print makes you landscape in the crowd.

  • Round neck design. The classic round neck with hood.
  • Great material. The polyester material keeps you warm in winter.
  • Regular fit. Loose-fitting design maximizes comfort.
  • Soft sleeve cuff and hem. Elastic and soft sleeve cuffs for fashion and comfort.
  • High quality print. Make unique pattern with high quality print.

 

 

SWEATER AND SWEATSHIRT
  • Material type: 60% cotton – 30% acrylic – 10% Spandex. Wool active fibre is used to react to your body’s temperature, thus keeping you warm in the Winter and cool in the Summer.
  • Print: Dye-sublimation printing, colors won’t fade or peel.
  • Wash care: Machine Wash Cold With Like Colors, Tumble Dry low if needed or lay flat to dry, use mild detergent, dry immediately.
  • Size and color: Our Size is Standard US Size. Also, If you are not sure of your size, Please read the Size Information of Product description in order to choose your own size!. Please do carefully refer to the size chart before purchasing. As different computers’ display leads to the color will have a little difference from the pictures.
 

TANK TOP AND SLEEVELESS

  • Size: This vest top is available in 8 sizes from S to 5XL. Please refer to our size chart in the product description or pictures and find your best fit.
  • Material: This lightweight men’s printed T-shirt is made of 100% high quality polyester material, the fabric is light and soft, suitable for everyday wear!
  • Design:The tank top is sleeveless and has a snug fit that sculpts the figure for a stylish look that will fit most body types. Men’s top will match well with variety of jeans, shorts,and will be a great gifts for your dad,brother and friends.
  • Occasion: The sleeveless t-shirt is perfect for daily wear in spring, summer, leisure, going out, beach, vacation, party, travel, shopping, etc.it is also suitable for various sports.
